citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4 pm on
16-Feb-17.
Animal Care Inspector left message on phone, honked car horn, and waited for 30 mins.
